---

## 4. `UnaryExecutor::Execute` writing string output into the result Vector heap

### 4a. Lambda form (closure can capture bind/local state)

**`/Users/tim_vergenz/code/personal/duckdb-jq/duckdb/src/function/scalar/string/regexp.cpp:230`** — most directly applicable to jq:

```cpp
if (info.constant_pattern) {
    auto &lstate = ExecuteFunctionState::GetFunctionState(state)->Cast<RegexLocalState>();
    UnaryExecutor::Execute<string_t, string_t>(strings, result, args.size(), [&](string_t input) {
        return Extract(input, result, lstate.constant_pattern, info.rewrite);
    });
}
```

